msgid "Drag and Drop"
msgstr "Drag and Drop"

#: ../../source/patterns/01_drag_and_drop.md:3
msgid ""
"To move an actor, you need to register the events `on_mouse_left` and "
"`on_mouse_left_released`. You also need a variable (e.g., `dragged`) to "
"store the state of whether an object is currently being dragged."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/patterns/01_drag_and_drop.md:6
msgid "When the mouse is clicked, the `dragged` variable is set to `True`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/patterns/01_drag_and_drop.md:7
msgid ""
"When the mouse is released, the actor is only moved if `dragged` is "
"`True`. Then `dragged` is reset to `False`."
msgstr ""

